                    <!-- /margin -->

                    <div class="margin">
                        <p>The video settings allow you to adjust the quality of all 3 videostreams of your camera. Please be adviced that high quality settings come with high requirements for your computer hardware and network bandwidth. Adjust the video quality to obtain a fluent video accordingly. Please refer to <a href="/Products/Indoor_Cameras/IN-6014_HD/Video_Streaming">RTSP Streaming</a> for accessing the cameras streams 2 and 3.</p>
